{"tid":475289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國會三議員晤林卓廷 允助跟進梁振英UGL案情","createTime":"2017-11-21T03:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T06:13:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c26488c970000a0baec66c18b12327d85baf0ce6","tid":475289,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511235134_d247.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511235134_d247.png&h=ffceb61f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511235136_fe98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511235136_fe98.png&h=b459d25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷在英國國會大樓先後會見了3名國會議員，包括工黨的Catherine West MP（Deputy Chair of The All Party Parliamentary Group on China）以及保守黨的Jeremy Lefroy MP 及Fiona Bruce MP，會面歷時近兩小時。<br />\n<br />\n3名國會議員都非常關注香港情況，林卓廷指出中英聯合聲明承諾的港人治港仍未落實，中央政府違反2017普選特首的承諾，推出假普選方案，但英國政府居然發表聲明呼籲港人接受，批評英國政府可恥（Disgraceful），同時指出英國作為中英聯合聲明締約國，有道義責任為香港發聲，要求中國政府履行聯合聲明。<br />\n<br />\n林亦反映人大釋法、新聞和學術自由倒退、廉政風暴等事件，顯示香港情況不容樂觀，最近政府及建制派多次提出要就《基本法》廿三條立法，憂慮中央可以藉此進一步收窄港人自由。<br />\n<br />\n3名議員都表示會密切留意香港情況，其中Catherine West MP表示有意訪華及到港，並同意協助跟進梁振英UGL案涉及英國管轄範圍的案情。Fiona Bruce MP則稱會聯繫其他關注香港的議員商討下一步行動。"},{"pid":"51fa7c9a642aafddbf170af14ad3e25deb6c1b55","tid":475289,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲信英國佬係幾on9"},{"pid":"2f2c78c57090cb20d1b74ba326b3c12d69fb50e9","tid":475289,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"搞鳩 689 就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acd239b365c0214317df082c475ff31cde19c39","tid":475289,"uid":34409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今時今日仲信英國佬係幾on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵習近平跟好冇？"}]}